#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.arctan2.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.arctan2"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:1 of
msgid "Element-wise arc tangent of ``x1/x2`` choosing the quadrant correctly."
msgstr "逐元素计算 ``x1/x2`` 的反正切值，并正确选择象限。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:3 of
msgid ""
"The quadrant (i.e., branch) is chosen so that ``arctan2(x1, x2)`` is the "
"signed angle in radians between the ray ending at the origin and passing "
"through the point (1,0), and the ray ending at the origin and passing "
"through the point (`x2`, `x1`).  (Note the role reversal: the "
"\"`y`-coordinate\" is the first function parameter, the "
"\"`x`-coordinate\" is the second.)  By IEEE convention, this function is "
"defined for `x2` = +/-0 and for either or both of `x1` and `x2` = +/-inf "
"(see Notes for specific values)."
msgstr ""
"选择象限（即分支），使得 ``arctan2(x1, x2)`` 是以弧度为单位的有符号角度，"
"该角度介于从原点出发经过点 (1,0) 的射线与从原点出发经过点 (`x2`, `x1`) 的"
"射线之间。（注意角色互换：第一个函数参数是 \"`y` 坐标\"，第二个是 \"`x` "
"坐标\"。）根据 IEEE 规范，此函数在 `x2` = +/-0 以及 `x1` 和/或 `x2` = +/-"
"inf 时有定义（具体值见注释）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:12 of
msgid ""
"This function is not defined for complex-valued arguments; for the so-"
"called argument of complex values, use `angle`."
msgstr "此函数不适用于复数值参数；对于复数值的所谓幅角，请使用 `angle`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2 of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:15 of
msgid "`y`-coordinates."
msgstr "`y` 坐标。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:17 of
msgid ""
"`x`-coordinates. `x2` must be broadcastable to match the shape of `x1` or"
" vice versa."
msgstr "`x` 坐标。`x2` 必须可以广播以匹配 `x1` 的形状，反之亦然。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:20 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有输入广播后的形状。如果未提供或为 "
"`None`，则返回一个新分配的 tensor。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:25 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的原值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2 of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:30 of
msgid "**angle** -- Array of angles in radians, in the range ``[-pi, pi]``."
msgstr "**angle** -- 以弧度为单位的角度数组，范围为 ``[-pi, pi]``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2 of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan2.arctan2:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`arctan`, :py:obj:`tan`, :py:obj:`angle`"
msgstr ""

