msgid ""
"*arctan2* is identical to the `atan2` function of the underlying C "
"library.  The following special values are defined in the C standard: "
"[1]_"
msgstr "*arctan2* 与底层 C 库的 `atan2` 函数相同。以下特殊值在 C 标准中定义：[1]_"

